{"tid":1404024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺高球場 「棕地研究」，須於2021年 第三季 完成","createTime":"2019-08-04T02:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T02:08:04.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76494b276da80233dd70982b0f87085874a34a05","tid":1404024,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"部分土地供應措施押後推出，但粉嶺高球場及棕地仍繼續。土木工程署就粉嶺高爾夫球場用地局部發展及新界北第一期研究，進行可行性研究的顧問費招標，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">料前者研究將於2021年第三季完成</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2410000/2414104/HKET_20190730_D01_02_aL_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2410000%2F2414104%2FHKET_20190730_D01_02_aL_1024.jpg&h=dcf8c7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高球場研究 料後年第3季完成<br />\n<br />\n當中屬於公眾支持度最高的棕地發展，政府在今年初已經決定提早就新界北發展區第一期進行可行性研究，以處理北區65公頃的棕地。據土木工程拓展署資料顯示，當局早前便邀請9間合資格顧問公司，遞交技術及顧問費建議書，並預計8月3日截止。（節錄）"},{"pid":"b64231aaedf3875ca4dfa3da1ccafb1c859aaae2","tid":1404024,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2414104/粉嶺高球場棕地%20研究招標%20料2021年第三季完成\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2414104%2F%E7%B2%89%E5%B6%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0%2520%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99%2520%E6%96%992021%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%A3%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=dad06487\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2414104/粉嶺高球場棕地%20研究招標%20料2021年第三季完成</a>"},{"pid":"7f42a5cfe565f70d08e773b499a557f6bb6f3332","tid":1404024,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}